OL,3,CVietnam's biggest fraudster faces
OL,4,Cdeath penalty, unless #7 billion repaid
OL,6,FThe death sentence for real estate
OL,7,Ftycoon Truong My Lan was upheld on
OL,8,FTuesday in Vietnam's largest fraud
OL,9,Fcase, the scale of which has raised
OL,10,Fconcerns about the country's wider
OL,11,Feconomy.
OL,13,FHowever, the court said her sentence
OL,14,Fcould be reduced to life in prison if
OL,15,Fshe reimburses three quarters of what
OL,16,Fshe took - equivalent to around #7
OL,17,Fbillion.
