OL,3,CVietnam's biggest fraudster faces
OL,4,Cdeath penalty, unless #7 billion repaid
OL,6,FLan was convicted of embezzlement and
OL,7,Fbribery over the fraud amounting to
OL,8,Faround #9 billion, nearly 3% of
OL,9,FVietnam's 2022 GDP.
OL,11,FAs chairperson of the Van Thinh Phat
OL,12,Freal estate firm, Lan illegally
OL,13,Fcontrolled Saigon Joint Stock
OL,14,FCommercial Bank between 2012 and 2022
OL,15,Fand allowed 2,500 loans that cost the
OL,16,Fbank #21 billion in losses.
