OL,3,CVietnam's biggest fraudster faces
OL,4,Cdeath penalty, unless #7 billion repaid
OL,6,FHer lawyers argued that she had repaid
OL,7,Fthe money, but the court disagreed
OL,8,Fsince there were legal issues with
OL,9,Fsome of the seized properties and
OL,10,Fprosecuting agencies couldn't assess
OL,11,Ftheir value, VN Express reported.
OL,13,FLan's lawyers also noted several
OL,14,Fmitigating circumstances; she had
OL,15,Fadmitted guilt, showed remorse and had
OL,16,Fpaid back part of the amount.
OL,18,F"I feel pained due to the waste of
OL,19,Fnational resources," she said last
OL,20,Fweek, state media reported.
