OL,3,CVietnam's biggest fraudster faces
OL,4,Cdeath penalty, unless #7 billion repaid
OL,6,FBut the court said her violations had
OL,7,Fnegatively impacted banking, caused
OL,8,Fpublic disorder and eroded people's
OL,9,Ftrust, VN Express said.
OL,11,FUnder Vietnamese law, death sentences
OL,12,Faren't carried out immediately and
OL,13,Fthere is an extended legal process,
OL,14,FNguyen Khac Giang, a visiting fellow
OL,15,Fat Singapore's ISEAS`Yusof Ishak
OL,16,FInstitute, said.
OL,18,FHe added that Lan could seek another
OL,19,Freview of the case or a presidential
OL,20,Fpardon to reduce her sentence.
