OL,3,CVietnam's biggest fraudster faces
OL,4,Cdeath penalty, unless #7 billion repaid
OL,6,F"Moreover, if she repays at least
OL,7,Fthree-quarters of the misappropriated
OL,8,Ffunds, the court may consider
OL,9,Fcommuting her sentence to life
OL,10,Fimprisonment," he said.
OL,12,FHer arrest was among the most high-
OL,13,Fprofile in an anti-corruption drive in
OL,14,FVietnam.
OL,16,FThe scale of her fraud shocked the
OL,17,Fnation with analysts raising questions
OL,18,Fabout the practices of other banks and
OL,19,Fbusinesses.
