OL,3,CVietnam's biggest fraudster faces
OL,4,Cdeath penalty, unless #7 billion repaid
OL,6,FLan and her family had set up the Van
OL,7,FThing Phat company in 1992 and it grew
OL,8,Finto one of Vietnam's richest real
OL,9,Festate firms, with luxury residential
OL,10,Fbuildings, offices, hotels and
OL,11,Fshopping centres.
OL,13,FThis made her a key player in the
OL,14,Fcountry's financial industry.
OL,16,FShe orchestrated the 2011 merger of
OL,17,Fthe SCB bank with two other lenders in
OL,18,Fcoordination with Vietnam's central
OL,19,Fbank.
