OL,3,CVietnam's biggest fraudster faces
OL,4,Cdeath penalty, unless #7 billion repaid
OL,6,FThe court said that she used this to
OL,7,Ftap SCB for cash and, according to
OL,8,Fgovernment documents, owned more than
OL,9,F90% of the bank while approving
OL,10,Fthousands of loans to "ghost
OL,11,Fcompanies."
OL,13,FThese loans, according to state media,
OL,14,Ffound their way to her and she bribed
OL,15,Fofficials to cover her tracks.
OL,17,FVietnam has handed down more than
OL,18,F2,000 death sentences in the past
OL,19,Fdecade and executed more than 400
OL,20,Fprisoners.
